{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2018/12/minuet-in-g-major/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/music/","name":"音乐"}],"tags":[{"name":"钢琴","path":"/tag/piano/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d310efdfd92749cb5455dc8690843173/e737e/cover-minuet.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d310efdfd92749cb5455dc8690843173/e737e/cover-minuet.jpg 800w,\n/static/d310efdfd92749cb5455dc8690843173/5bb6f/cover-minuet.jpg 1600w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d310efdfd92749cb5455dc8690843173/e7773/cover-minuet.webp 800w,\n/static/d310efdfd92749cb5455dc8690843173/f2fb1/cover-minuet.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2018/12/minuet-in-g-major/","date":"2018-12-20T05:51:58.000Z","excerpt":"今天来弹奏一首巴赫的小步舞曲G大调，Minuet in G Major。 此曲最开始是在巴赫Bach的第二任妻 … ","title":"钢琴演奏 – 巴赫的小步舞曲 in G大调","content":"\n<p>今天来弹奏一首<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"巴赫的小步舞曲 (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%8F%E6%AD%A5%E8%88%9E%E6%9B%B2_(%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%88)\" target=\"_blank\">巴赫的小步舞曲</a>G大调，<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Minuet in G Major (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%8F%E6%AD%A5%E8%88%9E%E6%9B%B2_(%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%88)\" target=\"_blank\">Minuet in G Major</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>此曲最开始是在巴赫Bach的第二任妻子安娜的笔记本中发现的，后来经证实是克里斯蒂安·佩尔德的作品。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>练习弹钢琴需要忍耐孤独，周末一整天独自练钢琴，不免会想练习的意义何在？我学习钢琴，是想重拾平静与专注，同时也是想弹奏美好的音乐给爱的人听。所以晓琴，这首小步舞曲送给你，也让那些所有孤独的练习有了意义。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>我总是在追寻某种意义……好，不多说，开始！</p>\n\n\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ntMX60eqklc\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>（在<a href=\"http://v.qq.com/x/page/a0810in3wo8.html\">腾讯视频</a>观看）</p>\n\n\n<p>还有键盘的顶视图</p>\n\n\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WAJUQw_iWRc\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>（在<a href=\"http://v.qq.com/x/page/q0810wdmop8.html\">腾讯视频</a>、<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzk1NzA2MzUyMA==.html?spm=a2hzp.8244740.0.0\">Youku</a>观看）</p>\n\n\n<p></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2018/12/minuet-in-g-major/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}